on doJump me
  [  0] getparam 0 .............................. <me>
  [  2] getchainedprop 67 ....................... <me.id>
  [  4] getchainedprop 66 ....................... <me.id.bigMe>
  [  6] pushsymb 22 ............................. <#none>
