  [ 76] getprop 77 .............................. <ancestor>
  [ 78] getparam 1 .............................. <sym>
  [ 80] pusharglist 2 ........................... <ancestor, sym>
  [ 82] objcall 803 ............................. <ancestor.getAnimSym(sym)>
  [ 85] pusharglistnoret 1 ...................... <ancestor.getAnimSym(sym)>
  [ 87] extcall 17 .............................. return ancestor.getAnimSym(sym)
  [ 89] ret
end

on goMode me, newMode
  [  0] getparam 1 .............................. <newMode>
  [  2] peek 0 .................................. case newMode of
  [  4] pushsymb 364 ............................ <#reel_fly>
  [  7] eq
